"```sql\nSELECT DisplayName, SUM(ViewCount) AS TotalViewCount\nFROM posts\nJOIN users ON posts.OwnerUserId = users.Id\nWHERE users.DisplayName IN ('Harvey Motulsky', 'Noah Snyder')\nGROUP BY DisplayName\nORDER BY TotalViewCount DESC\nLIMIT 1;\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the total view count for posts authored by either Harvey Motulsky or Noah Snyder. It then orders the results by the total view count in descending order and selects the user with the highest total view count, which indicates higher popularity."